Text: Thanks, but just FYI to everyone, I am highly suspicious of 95% of these actually being lossless.  Most of these tracks were never given a CD release, and therefor could not have been originally ripped to WAV or FLAC, so they were probably lossy mp3 sourced.  That being said, there are a lot of great tracks in this unofficial compilation (my favorite being "Kyle Petty, Son of Richard"), so feel free to grab it anyway.

The description is all wrong. 
These are not concert recordings. 
How do I know? I've posted the same album
that I encoded myself.
